WEBVTT

00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:06.967
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:29.000
CHILD:
There it is!

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.700
Gotcha!

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:36.300
[HUMMING]

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:43.734
All done.
What do you think?

00:01:43.734 --> 00:01:46.066
Your new outfit
is all ready, Bostov.

00:01:46.066 --> 00:01:49.166
See? Isn't it just the cutest
little thing ever?

00:01:49.166 --> 00:01:50.934
Wow, I just thought
of something else.

00:01:50.934 --> 00:01:52.533
Some colorful embroidery.

00:01:52.533 --> 00:01:53.800
Huh?

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:55.200
I'll use blue. No, red.

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:56.367
[GROANS]

00:01:56.367 --> 00:01:59.333
Since there's no red,
guess I'll use yellow!

00:01:59.333 --> 00:02:01.667
[GROANS] This is awful!

00:02:01.667 --> 00:02:03.800
I hate it when I don't have
the thread that I need.

00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:05.333
Don't worry, Bostov.

00:02:05.333 --> 00:02:07.767
I'm gonna buy some new thread
for your outfit right now.

00:02:07.767 --> 00:02:09.500
I'll be right back.

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:10.533
[HUMMING]

00:02:10.533 --> 00:02:13.433
Kon here. Day 175.

00:02:13.433 --> 00:02:15.266
As if it wasn't
humiliating enough

00:02:15.266 --> 00:02:18.567
having to live as a stupid stuff
animal trapped in this house,

00:02:18.567 --> 00:02:20.500
now I'm supposed to wear that?

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:22.433
After all the endless
hours I've been

00:02:22.433 --> 00:02:26.200
forced to actually play house
with the other stuffed animals?

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:28.734
I can't take it!
I'm outta here!

00:02:28.734 --> 00:02:31.233
Hey! What the hell? My hands!

00:02:31.233 --> 00:02:32.166
[SCREAMING]

00:02:32.166 --> 00:02:33.800
I've been stitched
into a threesome

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:34.800
with stupid and stupider!

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:37.133
How dare that human
do this to me?

00:02:37.133 --> 00:02:39.266
[SCREAMS]

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:47.667
The spirits are
always with you--

00:02:47.667 --> 00:02:49.500
CHILD:
I heard that
the squishy bug...

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:51.033
it'll make you really sick.

00:02:51.033 --> 00:02:53.533
CHILD 2:
Wow, I guess I shouldn't
have done that then, huh?

00:02:53.533 --> 00:02:55.800
Damn you kids! You totally
messed up my catch phrase.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:57.066
Once again, the spirits are--

00:02:57.066 --> 00:02:59.100
[MUMBLING]

00:02:59.100 --> 00:03:02.000
Customer parking only here
in front of the clinic.

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:03.567
Move that pile of junk.

00:03:03.567 --> 00:03:04.567
Hey, it's Karakura Red!

00:03:04.567 --> 00:03:06.200
Long time no see.

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:07.767
Not nearly long enough.

00:03:07.767 --> 00:03:09.233
What do you want, Don Kanonji?

00:03:09.233 --> 00:03:12.934
Oh, now is that any way to talk
to a friend, a comrade in arms

00:03:12.934 --> 00:03:15.333
who fought with you side
by side for peace and love

00:03:15.333 --> 00:03:16.633
in the free world?

00:03:16.633 --> 00:03:17.667
It's the middle of the day.

00:03:17.667 --> 00:03:19.667
Aren't you supposed
to be working?

00:03:19.667 --> 00:03:21.100
Hey, now!

00:03:21.100 --> 00:03:23.400
It may look like I'm unemployed,
but I can explain, kid.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.800
You see, TV shows are
taped weeks in advance,

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:27.734
so right now
I'm just on vacation.

00:03:27.734 --> 00:03:29.967
The fact is,
the network can't wait

00:03:29.967 --> 00:03:32.400
to renew my contract
for another season.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.533
[LAUGHS]

00:03:33.533 --> 00:03:34.467
That's funny.

00:03:34.467 --> 00:03:36.100
I heard you were
getting cancelled.

00:03:36.100 --> 00:03:37.233
Huh?

00:03:37.233 --> 00:03:39.633
I hear your ratings
have been really bad.

00:03:39.633 --> 00:03:40.900
Not so loud!

00:03:40.900 --> 00:03:43.066
If I lose one more sponsor,
I'll be back to selling

00:03:43.066 --> 00:03:44.767
used cars at midnight on cable!

00:03:44.767 --> 00:03:46.066
Never mind all that.

00:03:46.066 --> 00:03:48.967
I've come to enlist you
in a special training session!

00:03:48.967 --> 00:03:50.367
Oh, brother.

00:03:50.367 --> 00:03:51.467
What does that mean?

00:03:51.467 --> 00:03:52.800
I'll tell ya!

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:55.834
We need to train like crazy to
protect this happy little town

00:03:55.834 --> 00:03:58.467
from the bad spirits that
even now are threatening!

00:03:58.467 --> 00:03:59.633
Whoa!

00:03:59.633 --> 00:04:01.300
Almost lost my head there.

00:04:01.300 --> 00:04:02.233
Come on, Karakura Red.

00:04:02.233 --> 00:04:03.867
Let's start with
some jumping jacks!

00:04:03.867 --> 00:04:05.900
[LAUGHING]

00:04:05.900 --> 00:04:07.400
What's this really
all about?

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:08.867
Huh? Damn.

00:04:08.867 --> 00:04:11.600
It's painful to
admit, but it's true.

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:15.900
I, Don Kanonji, have seen
my popularity dropping lately.

00:04:15.900 --> 00:04:19.033
But anyone who thinks they've
seen the last of Don Kanonji

00:04:19.033 --> 00:04:20.433
has another thing comin'!

00:04:20.433 --> 00:04:23.066
I'll do whatever it takes
to revive this show,

00:04:23.066 --> 00:04:26.166
and I know just what I need to
grab the hearts of my audience.

00:04:26.166 --> 00:04:29.367
We all know everyone wants a
hero, so now all I have to do

00:04:29.367 --> 00:04:33.934
is bring back the
Karakura Superheroes!

00:04:33.934 --> 00:04:36.100
Waste of time, if you ask me.

00:04:36.100 --> 00:04:37.767
Huh? Ah!

00:04:37.767 --> 00:04:39.767
Hold on! No, wait!

00:04:39.767 --> 00:04:41.767
Please! Don't go!
I need you!

00:04:41.767 --> 00:04:43.200
I'm begging you,
Karakura Red!

00:04:43.200 --> 00:04:44.266
Please don't abandon me!

00:04:44.266 --> 00:04:46.433
Not now, in my time of need!

00:04:46.433 --> 00:04:50.000
Please! Please!

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.600
[LAUGHS]

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:53.233
On these wings of
freedom I shall now

00:04:53.233 --> 00:04:56.433
take flight, and soar
far away from here.

00:04:56.433 --> 00:04:58.700
Ah, they're freakin' heavy!

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:04.834
All right, fine, so I'm not
soaring so much as I'm walking.

00:05:04.834 --> 00:05:09.700
The point is,
I'm getting out of this-- ah!

00:05:09.700 --> 00:05:11.533
Damn, I've been spotted!

00:05:11.533 --> 00:05:12.967
Hello, there.

00:05:15.333 --> 00:05:17.133
[MUMBLING]

00:05:17.133 --> 00:05:18.300
I'm a robot.

00:05:18.300 --> 00:05:19.633
Look, a silver dollar!

00:05:19.633 --> 00:05:21.333
That's mine! Where? Ah!

00:05:21.333 --> 00:05:25.133
You are not a plain old
stuff animal, are you?

00:05:26.100 --> 00:05:27.467
Well, sure I am. Look.

00:05:27.467 --> 00:05:29.133
You just wind me up,
and I dance around

00:05:29.133 --> 00:05:30.200
like any other cheap toy--

00:05:30.200 --> 00:05:32.400
You're an evil spirit,
aren't you?

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:34.567
Oh, crap! I've had
about enough of this!

00:05:34.567 --> 00:05:36.400
I'm Bostov,
a stupid sailor suit wearing

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:37.767
prisoner of a little girl,

00:05:37.767 --> 00:05:40.066
sewn together with these
two yahoos, Buri and Puri.

00:05:40.066 --> 00:05:41.533
Now's my chance!

00:05:41.533 --> 00:05:43.667
Oh, no you don't!
Come back here!

00:05:43.667 --> 00:05:45.500
Hold it there, bad spirit.

00:05:45.500 --> 00:05:48.400
I'm curious about you. Hm?

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:49.667
What are you doing,
you freak?

00:05:49.667 --> 00:05:53.433
I'm no rose.
I-- ah, your nose breath!

00:05:53.433 --> 00:05:55.667
Well, you certainly have
a strange odor,

00:05:55.667 --> 00:05:57.934
but it's not awful.
I think I've got it.

00:05:57.934 --> 00:06:00.934
You're not an evil spirit.
You're just a weird spirit.

00:06:00.934 --> 00:06:02.000
Who are you calling weird,

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.834
you reject from
hell's marching band?

00:06:03.834 --> 00:06:06.834
As every TV action fan knows,
no team of superheroes

00:06:06.834 --> 00:06:08.967
can be complete
without a mascot.

00:06:08.967 --> 00:06:10.767
This walking,
stalking stuffed animal

00:06:10.767 --> 00:06:13.300
could be just the thing to put
the Karakura superheroes

00:06:13.300 --> 00:06:14.533
over the top!

00:06:14.533 --> 00:06:15.700
[LAUGHS]

00:06:15.700 --> 00:06:17.567
Whatever the hell
you're planning for me,

00:06:17.567 --> 00:06:18.734
you can forget about it.

00:06:18.734 --> 00:06:21.133
Oh, good heavens. Did I
say all of that out loud?

00:06:21.133 --> 00:06:22.600
It must be old age
kicking in.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:23.900
I hardly even
know my own name,

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:25.533
much less what
I'm blabbering about.

00:06:25.533 --> 00:06:27.066
What are you
blabbering about?

00:06:27.066 --> 00:06:31.100
I'll tell you! How would you
like to become an actual hero?

00:06:31.100 --> 00:06:33.567
A hero? For real?

00:06:33.567 --> 00:06:37.133
Yes. A hero of justice.

00:06:37.133 --> 00:06:39.166
A hero of justice, huh?

00:06:39.166 --> 00:06:40.567
[GASPS]

00:06:40.567 --> 00:06:43.033
Oh, Kon, you're the best!
Wow!

00:06:43.033 --> 00:06:47.066
This must be heaven, squeezed
by so many lovely marshmallows!

00:06:47.066 --> 00:06:49.367
So, what do you say?

00:06:49.367 --> 00:06:50.900
Do you think you're
ready to join

00:06:50.900 --> 00:06:52.166
the superheroes of justice?

00:06:55.367 --> 00:06:59.667
My name is Kon, also
known as Karakura King!

00:07:01.567 --> 00:07:03.233
[LAUGHS]

00:07:04.667 --> 00:07:06.867
Welcome aboard,
new member.

00:07:06.867 --> 00:07:08.667
Hi!
Huh?

00:07:08.667 --> 00:07:10.233
Don Kanonji!

00:07:10.233 --> 00:07:12.133
[LAUGHS]

00:07:12.133 --> 00:07:14.867
[LAUGHS]

00:07:14.867 --> 00:07:16.400
[LAUGHING]

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:20.000
Oh, it has little a while,
sister of Ichigo.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.367
Are you here to do
a Spirit Hunter episode?

00:07:22.367 --> 00:07:24.667
Oh, no. I'm here
recruiting the latest member

00:07:24.667 --> 00:07:26.867
for my team of superheroes.

00:07:26.867 --> 00:07:28.834
Really? Who is that?

00:07:28.834 --> 00:07:30.300
Let me introduce you.

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:33.300
Here he is, the newest member
of the Karakura Superheroes,

00:07:33.300 --> 00:07:35.233
Karakura King!

00:07:35.233 --> 00:07:36.166
Huh?

00:07:36.166 --> 00:07:37.800
You mean
this stuffed animal?

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:38.767
Oh, no, no, no, no, no.

00:07:38.767 --> 00:07:41.000
Tell me this isn't happening.

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:42.433
Hm.

00:07:42.433 --> 00:07:44.900
You sure look a lot like
a friend of mine.

00:07:44.900 --> 00:07:46.500
Nice to meet ya.

00:07:46.500 --> 00:07:48.300
N-nice to meet you, too.

00:07:48.300 --> 00:07:50.834
You even talk.
That's amazing!

00:07:50.834 --> 00:07:53.166
How about you,
Karakura Yellow?

00:07:53.166 --> 00:07:54.967
You'll join up too,
right?

00:07:54.967 --> 00:07:57.166
Absolutely! Yes, sir!
Affirmative! Oh?

00:07:57.166 --> 00:08:00.767
Hey, I have a new outfit
I made for Bostov's boyfriend

00:08:00.767 --> 00:08:02.934
that might be
just right.

00:08:02.934 --> 00:08:04.967
What do you think,
Karakura King?

00:08:04.967 --> 00:08:06.033
Huh?

00:08:06.033 --> 00:08:07.533
You've got to be kidding me.

00:08:07.533 --> 00:08:10.934
All this time I've been
wearing frilly dresses,

00:08:10.934 --> 00:08:13.934
I could have been dressed
like a bad ass superhero?

00:08:13.934 --> 00:08:17.767
I wish I knew she could
make outfits like this.

00:08:17.767 --> 00:08:19.000
Oh!

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:20.600
Ooh!
Ah!

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:22.100
How do I look?

00:08:22.100 --> 00:08:23.567
You look so cool,
Karakura King!

00:08:23.567 --> 00:08:25.166
It fits perfectly!

00:08:25.166 --> 00:08:28.166
That makes one member
and a mascot.

00:08:28.166 --> 00:08:30.900
If only I could pull the rest
of them out of the ground...

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:32.667
Just like a bunch of taters!

00:08:32.667 --> 00:08:35.333
What's a bunch of taters?
Did I say that out loud, too?

00:08:35.333 --> 00:08:38.100
I gotta watch that.
Never mind. Everything is okay!

00:08:38.100 --> 00:08:39.867
[LAUGHS]

00:08:44.033 --> 00:08:45.333
There it is.

00:08:49.934 --> 00:08:52.100
So Karin
turned you down, huh?

00:08:52.100 --> 00:08:54.333
Yes, but it doesn't matter.
I think we go left here.

00:08:54.333 --> 00:08:56.367
Okay.

00:08:56.367 --> 00:08:57.567
[GASPS]
KON: Uh-oh!

00:08:57.567 --> 00:08:59.467
I forgot she didn't
know I could walk.

00:08:59.467 --> 00:09:00.667
Oh, well.

00:09:00.667 --> 00:09:03.333
If she hasn't recognized
me by now, she won't.

00:09:03.333 --> 00:09:05.500
I have never seen
a stuffed animal that walks.

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:07.333
What did you expect
of the Karakura King?

00:09:07.333 --> 00:09:08.333
Amazing!

00:09:08.333 --> 00:09:10.066
Hey, I can jump rope
double dutch, too.

00:09:10.066 --> 00:09:12.233
Even more amazing!

00:09:12.233 --> 00:09:14.533
All my friend Bostov ever
does is sit around in my room

00:09:14.533 --> 00:09:16.300
and sleep all the time.

00:09:16.300 --> 00:09:17.867
But for the most part,
I think I know

00:09:17.867 --> 00:09:19.633
what she's dreaming about.

00:09:19.633 --> 00:09:21.400
She thinks about
having a boyfriend,

00:09:21.400 --> 00:09:22.433
or pretty girls' clothes.

00:09:22.433 --> 00:09:24.533
Girls without clothes,
you mean.

00:09:24.533 --> 00:09:26.300
Soon my heroic team
will be complete,

00:09:26.300 --> 00:09:28.500
and my resurrection can begin!

00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:30.533
That's right!
Whatever he just said!

00:09:30.533 --> 00:09:31.633
Look out!
Huh?

00:09:32.467 --> 00:09:35.700
Wah!
What's the big idea?

00:09:35.700 --> 00:09:39.000
Hey, there's still
more trash up here! Huh?

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:42.767
YUZU:
Why'd you throw trash
on those people?

00:09:42.767 --> 00:09:44.400
I know this place.

00:09:47.100 --> 00:09:48.166
So what kind of training?

00:09:48.166 --> 00:09:49.700
I'm glad you asked
that question.

00:09:49.700 --> 00:09:50.600
You should join us!

00:09:50.600 --> 00:09:54.100
I love how you talk.
Oh?

00:09:54.100 --> 00:09:55.500
You've gotta be kidding!

00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:59.233
The last time I helped you guys,
I was grounded for six months!

00:09:59.233 --> 00:10:00.300
Oh, please?

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:02.467
I've got nothing against
you, Yuzu. But you?

00:10:02.467 --> 00:10:04.166
I'll never take
orders from you again!

00:10:04.166 --> 00:10:06.200
Oh?
Got that?

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:08.300
For sure?

00:10:08.300 --> 00:10:12.900
Somehow I know I'm going
to regret this, but okay.

00:10:12.900 --> 00:10:16.033
Karakura Red, here we go again!

00:10:16.033 --> 00:10:18.500
Jinta, remember what Tessai
does when you goof off?

00:10:18.500 --> 00:10:22.166
[SCREAMING]

00:10:22.166 --> 00:10:24.633
You're right.
I never want to feel that again.

00:10:24.633 --> 00:10:26.467
It'll be okay if we do
it together, though.

00:10:26.467 --> 00:10:28.000
Huh?

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:30.900
And we'll be doing something
to help out our neighborhood.

00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:32.300
Right?

00:10:32.300 --> 00:10:34.900
Oh, all right, all right!

00:10:34.900 --> 00:10:36.500
I'll do it,
I'll do it, I'll do it!

00:10:36.500 --> 00:10:38.033
Ururu, you're joining, too.

00:10:38.033 --> 00:10:40.633
Then if we get in trouble,
we'll both get it equally.

00:10:40.633 --> 00:10:42.400
I don't know.
Please, Ururu?

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:44.867
It'll be fun. Okay?

00:10:44.867 --> 00:10:46.233
All right.

00:10:46.233 --> 00:10:49.734
KON:
What kind of a nightmare
superhero team is this?

00:10:49.734 --> 00:10:52.734
A goofball in a clown suit,
a psycho runt, a space cadet?

00:10:52.734 --> 00:10:54.867
and a monster
disguised as a girl?

00:10:54.867 --> 00:10:57.066
[LAUGHTER]

00:10:57.066 --> 00:10:58.600
You guys have got
to be kidding me!

00:10:58.600 --> 00:11:00.667
I can't work with these losers.
I'm outta here.

00:11:00.667 --> 00:11:02.000
Wah!

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:04.467
[TOGETHER]:
And just where do you
think you're going?

00:11:04.467 --> 00:11:05.734
Let's start training.

00:11:05.734 --> 00:11:09.233
You wouldn't want to miss out
on that, now, would you?

00:11:09.233 --> 00:11:11.033
No! Of course not!

00:11:11.033 --> 00:11:13.133
I was just about
to suggest that, myself!

00:11:15.934 --> 00:11:19.400
All right! Let's get this
training session started!

00:11:19.400 --> 00:11:21.667
Karakura King,
are you ready?

00:11:21.667 --> 00:11:25.100
What is this supposed to
be training me for, exactly?

00:11:25.100 --> 00:11:27.600
Ten... nine...

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:29.333
eight, seven, six,
five, four, three,

00:11:29.333 --> 00:11:30.533
two, one, blast off!

00:11:30.533 --> 00:11:32.834
[SCREAMING]

00:11:32.834 --> 00:11:35.033
First exercise
successful!

00:11:35.033 --> 00:11:37.133
We did it!
Good job!

00:11:39.633 --> 00:11:40.867
Now what am I learning?

00:11:40.867 --> 00:11:42.200
Learning to be fabulous!

00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:44.800
What does that have
to do with anything?

00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:46.066
Whoa!

00:11:46.066 --> 00:11:48.100
I'm a superhero,
not a giant wedding cake!

00:11:48.100 --> 00:11:50.767
[TOGETHER]:
Karakura King,
a big and beautiful thing!

00:11:50.767 --> 00:11:52.166
KON:
Song and dance?

00:11:52.166 --> 00:11:54.667
[TOGETHER]:
Karakura King,
a big and beautiful thing!

00:11:54.667 --> 00:11:57.266
What's this string?
Oh, you shouldn't pull on that.

00:11:57.266 --> 00:11:59.300
You should have said
that before I pulled.

00:11:59.300 --> 00:12:01.433
You shouldn't have
pulled before you asked.

00:12:01.433 --> 00:12:03.667
Huh? Ah!

00:12:03.667 --> 00:12:05.900
This is not training!
This is torture!

00:12:05.900 --> 00:12:11.200
Ah! Why does everything
happen to me?

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:12.700
Marvelous!

00:12:12.700 --> 00:12:13.667
A failure.

00:12:13.667 --> 00:12:15.033
Oh, really?
You think so?

00:12:15.033 --> 00:12:17.200
It would have been
a lot prettier at night.

00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:19.467
I get blown up,
and that's all you care about?

00:12:19.467 --> 00:12:21.200
I don't have to put
up with this abuse!

00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:23.066
I'm through with your training!

00:12:23.066 --> 00:12:24.166
[SHOUTING]

00:12:24.166 --> 00:12:25.233
Wait, Karakura King!

00:12:25.233 --> 00:12:27.467
KON:
See ya, losers!

00:12:27.467 --> 00:12:30.333
[GROANING]

00:12:30.333 --> 00:12:31.433
This headache.

00:12:31.433 --> 00:12:33.934
It must be about to rain,
or something.

00:12:35.467 --> 00:12:36.800
Yuzu?

00:12:36.800 --> 00:12:38.233
Not here.

00:12:38.233 --> 00:12:39.367
Where'd she go?

00:12:42.433 --> 00:12:44.233
Rukia, where are you?

00:12:44.233 --> 00:12:45.800
Please come back.

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:48.000
I need you to hold me
and save me from these monsters.

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:50.533
You don't know the horrors
they're putting me through here.

00:12:50.533 --> 00:12:53.400
[SOBBING]:
Come home, Rukia!

00:12:53.400 --> 00:12:54.400
Huh?

00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:55.633
[YELPING]

00:12:55.633 --> 00:12:57.367
No! No! No! No!

00:12:57.367 --> 00:12:59.367
No! No! No! No!

00:12:59.367 --> 00:13:01.633
Karakura King!

00:13:01.633 --> 00:13:03.333
Karakura King?

00:13:03.333 --> 00:13:05.333
Karakura King?

00:13:05.333 --> 00:13:06.734
Where did he go?

00:13:06.734 --> 00:13:08.667
Hm.

00:13:08.667 --> 00:13:11.600
Disaster, crisis!

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:13.266
Spine-tingling suspense.

00:13:13.266 --> 00:13:15.300
Just when things
were going along so well,

00:13:15.300 --> 00:13:17.166
fate has reared its
ugly head with the loss

00:13:17.166 --> 00:13:19.233
my super team's lovable mascot.

00:13:19.233 --> 00:13:21.734
My perfect plan lies in ruins!

00:13:21.734 --> 00:13:22.934
What will I do?

00:13:22.934 --> 00:13:25.066
Have you guys noticed?

00:13:25.066 --> 00:13:26.900
He keeps talking to himself?

00:13:26.900 --> 00:13:28.867
A lot.
Huh?

00:13:28.867 --> 00:13:31.066
I'm not about to give
up on the king yet.

00:13:31.066 --> 00:13:33.467
But we haven't found
a trace of him anywhere.

00:13:33.467 --> 00:13:35.133
If only he'd give us a sign.

00:13:35.133 --> 00:13:36.533
KON [SCREAMING]:
Help me!

00:13:36.533 --> 00:13:37.500
There he is!

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:40.500
KON:
Help! Help! It's got me!

00:13:40.500 --> 00:13:42.066
That is one big, bad spirit!

00:13:42.066 --> 00:13:43.000
Whoa, it's a hollow!

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:46.400
Way to go, Karakura King!
Huh?

00:13:46.400 --> 00:13:48.266
What are you
talking about, girl?

00:13:48.266 --> 00:13:50.166
Karakura King can fly, too.

00:13:50.166 --> 00:13:51.934
Isn't he just the coolest?

00:13:51.934 --> 00:13:53.166
KANONJI:
Oh, I forgot.

00:13:53.166 --> 00:13:55.166
You can't see him, can you?

00:13:55.166 --> 00:13:56.300
Well, it doesn't matter.

00:13:56.300 --> 00:13:58.533
With big trouble
brewing and dark clouds

00:13:58.533 --> 00:13:59.600
gathering on the horizon.

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:01.367
But when evil rears
its ugly head,

00:14:01.367 --> 00:14:03.000
there's only one thing to do.

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:07.233
And Don Kanonji
is just the man to do it!

00:14:07.233 --> 00:14:09.533
I love the sound
of my own voice!

00:14:09.533 --> 00:14:12.333
So, the first mission for
the newly reformed

00:14:12.333 --> 00:14:15.266
Karakura Superheroes
is to save the Karakura King!

00:14:15.266 --> 00:14:17.600
Yes, sir!
All right!

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:19.066
Help me!

00:14:19.066 --> 00:14:20.133
[SCREAMING]

00:14:23.867 --> 00:14:26.133
[SCREAMING]

00:14:26.834 --> 00:14:27.934
[NERVOUS LAUGH]

00:14:27.934 --> 00:14:29.500
Don't eat me!
Don't eat me, please!

00:14:29.500 --> 00:14:30.800
I'm not very tasty.

00:14:30.800 --> 00:14:33.066
I'm just full of
cotton on the inside.

00:14:33.066 --> 00:14:34.233
Ha, ha, ha.

00:14:34.233 --> 00:14:37.500
Oh, I have no intention
of eating you.

00:14:37.500 --> 00:14:40.467
What is this?
You mean you can actually talk?

00:14:40.467 --> 00:14:42.033
Of course I can.

00:14:42.033 --> 00:14:44.433
Well, what are you planning
to do with me, then?

00:14:44.433 --> 00:14:46.367
I'm going to take you
back home with me

00:14:46.367 --> 00:14:48.033
and give you good lovin'.

00:14:48.033 --> 00:14:50.133
I think that might be
worse than getting eaten!

00:14:50.133 --> 00:14:53.467
HOLLOW:
Come on, my little
flat faced lion.

00:14:53.467 --> 00:14:55.834
No, no! No, let me go!

00:14:55.834 --> 00:14:58.667
You don't have to do
so afraid, little one.

00:14:58.667 --> 00:15:00.500
I'm a professional, you know?

00:15:00.500 --> 00:15:04.767
-Oh, I can't believe it's really
going to end like this for me.

00:15:04.767 --> 00:15:06.934
Goodbye, my fair Rukia.

00:15:06.934 --> 00:15:08.300
Goodbye, my sweet Orihime.

00:15:08.300 --> 00:15:09.934
Farewell to all
the beautiful girls

00:15:09.934 --> 00:15:13.934
I never had a chance to meet!

00:15:13.934 --> 00:15:14.967
Aw.

00:15:14.967 --> 00:15:17.400
Please make it painless.

00:15:17.400 --> 00:15:19.567
Hold it right there!
What?

00:15:19.567 --> 00:15:22.400
Oh, good! About time you
came to rescue me!

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:25.467
[SHOUTING]

00:15:25.467 --> 00:15:26.867
This is a rescue?

00:15:26.867 --> 00:15:29.734
The spirits are
always with you!

00:15:29.734 --> 00:15:32.233
[LAUGHING]

00:15:39.100 --> 00:15:42.400
The burning heart
is the flame of justice!

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:46.033
Burning eternal
fire, Karakura Red!

00:15:46.033 --> 00:15:49.967
I'm Karakura Pink.

00:15:49.967 --> 00:15:52.967
Um, I, oh, right.
Introductions.

00:15:52.967 --> 00:15:56.533
Well, I'm Yellow.
And there's Karakura King!

00:15:56.533 --> 00:15:58.066
How ridiculous you are.

00:15:58.066 --> 00:15:59.967
And so foolish,
to think you could stop

00:15:59.967 --> 00:16:01.266
the love affair
I've begun.

00:16:01.266 --> 00:16:03.600
Little flat face
is all mine now.

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:06.166
Oh, no! It's even changed my
name already!

00:16:06.166 --> 00:16:10.667
HOLLOW:
Anyone who messes with
my love life gets sliced!

00:16:10.667 --> 00:16:13.400
I don't understand.
What's happening?

00:16:13.400 --> 00:16:15.333
Yuzu, no! Get away!

00:16:15.333 --> 00:16:16.567
She can't
see the Hollow.

00:16:16.567 --> 00:16:18.200
Well, look here.
A willing victim?

00:16:18.200 --> 00:16:20.266
Where-- where did everyone go?

00:16:20.266 --> 00:16:22.734
Do you want to taste my claw?

00:16:22.734 --> 00:16:23.967
Run away!

00:16:23.967 --> 00:16:25.567
Tear at flesh, my claw!

00:16:25.567 --> 00:16:28.467
Yuzu!
Karakura Yellow!

00:16:28.467 --> 00:16:29.900
[GASPING]

00:16:33.433 --> 00:16:35.133
Hey, Karin!

00:16:35.133 --> 00:16:36.233
That was close.

00:16:37.467 --> 00:16:41.100
No wonder I've been
having headaches.

00:16:41.100 --> 00:16:44.333
Well, Karakura Red. You've come
to join us after all.

00:16:44.333 --> 00:16:46.066
Hey, I'm Karakura Red!

00:16:46.066 --> 00:16:48.233
Don't tell me you guys
are still doing that stuff

00:16:48.233 --> 00:16:50.100
and calling yourselves
those silly names.

00:16:50.100 --> 00:16:51.667
Listen, I joined
because there were

00:16:51.667 --> 00:16:52.900
people who
needed our help.

00:16:52.900 --> 00:16:55.066
What's with
Karakura King?

00:16:55.066 --> 00:16:56.567
Stealthy.

00:16:56.567 --> 00:16:58.800
Isn't that Yuzu's Bostov doll?

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:01.066
No, that's
Karakura King.

00:17:01.066 --> 00:17:03.100
Karakura King needs
our help, Karin.

00:17:03.100 --> 00:17:04.900
And you're just
the one to do it.

00:17:04.900 --> 00:17:06.500
You don't know what
you're asking for.

00:17:06.500 --> 00:17:09.633
But where are
you my lover lion?

00:17:09.633 --> 00:17:12.133
Wait for me!

00:17:12.133 --> 00:17:13.133
My sweetheart!

00:17:13.133 --> 00:17:14.600
Oh, don't leave me, my love.

00:17:14.600 --> 00:17:17.700
All right! Then I'll go take
care of this monster myself!

00:17:17.700 --> 00:17:19.000
Huh? Oh, no you don't!

00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:20.066
Wait, you guys!

00:17:20.066 --> 00:17:21.467
What do you think
you're doing?

00:17:21.467 --> 00:17:23.633
I'm not about to leave
this all up to you!

00:17:23.633 --> 00:17:25.133
You've got some nerve,
mocking me!

00:17:25.133 --> 00:17:27.600
You're the one who put Yuzu
in danger in the first place.

00:17:27.600 --> 00:17:29.166
Oh, shut up,
shut up, shut up!

00:17:29.166 --> 00:17:30.500
What would
you know about it?

00:17:30.500 --> 00:17:32.133
You're just a girl!

00:17:32.133 --> 00:17:33.066
Oh, no you didn't!

00:17:33.066 --> 00:17:34.734
Oh, yes I did!

00:17:34.734 --> 00:17:36.700
[BOTH SCREAMING]

00:17:36.700 --> 00:17:38.533
HOLLOW:
Wait, flat face!

00:17:38.533 --> 00:17:39.600
Huh?

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.834
[SCREAMING]

00:17:42.834 --> 00:17:45.266
HOLLOW:
Leave him alone! He's mine!

00:17:45.266 --> 00:17:47.433
Just get away from me,
all of you!

00:17:47.433 --> 00:17:48.633
Now I've got you!

00:17:48.633 --> 00:17:50.200
[TOGETHER]:
You stay out of this!

00:17:53.734 --> 00:17:55.266
I told you to let
me handle this!

00:17:55.266 --> 00:17:57.433
Let you mess it up,
you mean!

00:17:57.433 --> 00:17:59.233
That's your job, clown!

00:17:59.233 --> 00:18:01.767
How dare you call me clown!

00:18:01.767 --> 00:18:03.266
[HOLLOW GROANS]

00:18:03.266 --> 00:18:06.133
You little twerp!
Look who's talking, wannabe!

00:18:06.133 --> 00:18:09.400
Shut up, stupid!
You're stupid!

00:18:09.400 --> 00:18:11.734
Oh, yeah? Well, you're stupid
for calling me stupid.

00:18:11.734 --> 00:18:13.500
Oh, really?
Stupid!

00:18:13.500 --> 00:18:18.066
Silence, both of you!
Enough of your bickering!

00:18:18.066 --> 00:18:20.734
I've had it with you
annoying creatures!

00:18:20.734 --> 00:18:24.133
I'm going to release my
twister and destroy you!

00:18:24.133 --> 00:18:25.266
[SCREAMING]

00:18:25.266 --> 00:18:26.300
KANONJI:
A typhoon!

00:18:26.300 --> 00:18:28.567
What did I do to deserve this?

00:18:33.567 --> 00:18:35.700
Yuzu! Take my hand!

00:18:35.700 --> 00:18:38.266
Yuzu!

00:18:38.266 --> 00:18:40.333
They're all falling
right into the center.

00:18:40.333 --> 00:18:42.967
KON:
I'm spinning and swirling!
I'm getting sucked in!

00:18:42.967 --> 00:18:43.900
Oh, wow.

00:18:43.900 --> 00:18:47.266
I guess I'm all right,
after all.

00:18:47.266 --> 00:18:50.000
The Hollow is
down at the center.

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:52.767
I've got to throw
a really powerful attack.

00:18:52.767 --> 00:18:54.300
Huh? What now?

00:18:54.300 --> 00:18:56.767
[MUMBLING]

00:18:56.767 --> 00:18:58.033
What have you done to me?

00:18:58.033 --> 00:19:01.100
Do it, Ururu!
Huh? What are you gonna do?

00:19:01.100 --> 00:19:04.567
Karakura Storm Serve!

00:19:04.567 --> 00:19:07.734
[KON SCREAMING]

00:19:07.734 --> 00:19:10.900
Now it's our turn, Karin!
Home run!

00:19:14.133 --> 00:19:15.467
I got it!

00:19:17.967 --> 00:19:20.633
[SCREAMS]

00:19:20.633 --> 00:19:22.467
Goal kick!

00:19:22.467 --> 00:19:25.000
Why me?

00:19:25.900 --> 00:19:28.133
Huh? The technique!

00:19:28.133 --> 00:19:30.533
I think they're using
the legendary

00:19:30.533 --> 00:19:34.934
Karakura Ultimate Buster Attack!
Yow!

00:19:34.934 --> 00:19:37.233
I guess this is the end for me.

00:19:37.233 --> 00:19:43.100
I can see eternity
reaching out to suck me in.

00:19:43.100 --> 00:19:48.066
How humiliating
to have it end this way!

00:19:48.066 --> 00:19:50.433
Where is everyone?
Up there.

00:19:50.433 --> 00:19:54.367
[KANONJI LAUGHING]

00:19:54.367 --> 00:19:55.433
Listen here, you pervert!

00:19:55.433 --> 00:19:57.934
You put me down right
now, you hear me?

00:20:02.900 --> 00:20:06.900
Is, is this heaven?

00:20:06.900 --> 00:20:10.467
If it is, then are you an angel?

00:20:10.467 --> 00:20:12.166
Oh. Obviously not.

00:20:12.166 --> 00:20:14.500
Are you gonna be all right,
Karakura King?

00:20:14.500 --> 00:20:17.867
Well, I'm alive,
if that's what you mean.

00:20:17.867 --> 00:20:19.100
Thank goodness.

00:20:19.100 --> 00:20:21.467
For a minute there, I thought
you sacrificed yourself

00:20:21.467 --> 00:20:23.266
to save all the rest of us.

00:20:23.266 --> 00:20:26.367
Oh, yeah. That was my plan
right from the beginning. Sure.

00:20:26.367 --> 00:20:28.166
Now you see the
impressive results

00:20:28.166 --> 00:20:31.200
of all our hard training!
Magnificent!

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:35.000
[LAUGHING]

00:20:35.000 --> 00:20:37.200
The spirits are always with you!

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:40.300
Yeah!
[CHEERING]

00:20:40.300 --> 00:20:41.567
SPECIAL INVESTIGATIVE REPORT

00:20:41.567 --> 00:20:43.600
All right. Welcome
to a special edition report,

00:20:43.600 --> 00:20:46.700
in which I, Don Kanonji,
join the legendary superheroes

00:20:46.700 --> 00:20:49.066
of Karakura town
on a brave mission

00:20:49.066 --> 00:20:50.433
into the uncharted wilderness!

00:20:50.433 --> 00:20:53.066
Shock and suspense!

00:20:53.066 --> 00:20:55.000
AUDIENCE:
Shock and suspense!

00:20:55.000 --> 00:20:57.266
Huh? Hey, Karin!

00:20:57.266 --> 00:20:59.600
Take a look at what's on
the television right now.

00:20:59.600 --> 00:21:01.467
It's you!
Huh?

00:21:01.467 --> 00:21:03.600
What the--
When did he shoot this?

00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:04.800
Oh, the joy of it.

00:21:04.800 --> 00:21:06.800
Here you see one of the
tortured evil spirits

00:21:06.800 --> 00:21:08.100
that can never rest!

00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:12.333
I wonder how
Karakura King is doing. Huh?

00:21:12.333 --> 00:21:15.533
But don't be sad, Bostov.
I haven't forgotten you.

00:21:15.533 --> 00:21:17.400
I'm making you a
brand new outfit

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:18.967
so you'll be even prettier.

00:21:18.967 --> 00:21:25.433
Oh, joy.
I can hardly wait.

