Worried ♪

00:21:47.300 --> 00:21:51.667
♪ Keep your head right up ♪

00:21:51.667 --> 00:21:52.767
♪ To the sky ♪

00:21:52.767 --> 00:21:54.967
♪ No matter when ♪
