♪ All right ♪

00:22:24.133 --> 00:22:25.900
♪ Happypeople ♪

00:22:25.900 --> 00:22:28.233
♪ Mmm, happy ♪

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:32.433
[KANONJI LAUGHING]

00:22:32.433 --> 00:22:34.767
For all of you plagued
by bad spirits,

00:22:34.767 --> 00:22:36.533
we, the Karakura Superheroes,

00:22:36.533 --> 00:22:38.934
can take care of your problems
right away!

00:22:38.934 --> 00:22:40.266
Call now to take
advantage of our

00:22:40.266 --> 00:22:42.133
no money down, interest free
offer!

00:22:42.133 --> 00:22:45.433
ICHIGO:
Next episode, we're getting
back to our main story!

